        ✕
      </button>

      <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Reserve Your Seat</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl mt-1">Booking Request</h3>
          <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-300 mt-1 font-light leading-relaxed">Fill out your contact details. Our team will verify slot availability and contact you via WhatsApp for deposit details.</p>
